{"openapi":"3.0.0","info":{"title":"Murojaat24 API","description":"\n## Kommunal xizmatlar murojaatlari tizimi\n\nMurojaat24 - Termiz shahri fuqarolarining kommunal xizmatlarga oid murojaatlarini qabul qilish va boshqarish tizimi.\n\n### Autentifikatsiya\n- Xodimlar **parol** orqali tizimga kiradi\n- Parolni unutgan bo'lsa **SMS OTP** orqali tiklash mumkin\n- Token cookie orqali saqlanadi (httpOnly)\n\n### Fuqarolar uchun\n- Murojaat yuborishdan oldin **telefon raqam OTP** orqali tasdiqlanadi\n- Murojaat holatini kuzatish uchun ro'yxatdan o'tish talab qilinmaydi\n\n### Foydalanuvchi rollari\n- **Admin** - Tizimni to'liq boshqarish\n- **Manager** - Murojaatlarni nazorat qilish, tasdiqlash\n- **Dispatcher** - Mutaxassislarni tayinlash\n- **Operator** - Murojaatlarni qabul qilish\n- **Specialist** - Murojaatlarni bajarish\n\n### Murojaat holatlari\n- 🔵 **new** - Yangi murojaat\n- 🟠 **assigned** - Mutaxassis tayinlangan\n- 🟡 **in-progress** - Bajarilmoqda\n- 🟢 **completed** - Yakunlangan\n- ✅ **verified** - Tasdiqlangan\n- 🔴 **rejected** - Rad etilgan\n      ","version":"1.0.0","contact":{"name":"Murojaat24 Support","email":"support@murojaat24.uz"}},"components":{"securitySchemes":{"cookieAuth":{"type":"apiKey","in":"cookie","name":"access_token","description":"JWT token cookie orqali"}},"schemas":{"Error":{"type":"object","properties":{"success":{"type":"boolean","example":false},"message":{"type":"string","example":"Xatolik yuz berdi"}}},"User":{"type":"object","properties":{"_id":{"type":"string"},"phone":{"type":"string","example":"+998901234567"},"role":{"type":"string","enum":["operator","dispatcher","specialist","manager","admin"]},"profile":{"type":"object","properties":{"firstName":{"type":"string"},"lastName":{"type":"string"},"avatar":{"type":"string"}}},"organization":{"type":"string"},"quarter":{"type":"string"},"sector":{"type":"string"},"specialization":{"type":"string"},"status":{"type":"string","enum":["active","inactive","busy"]}}},"Request":{"type":"o